message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.SI. This paper is focused on peer review in the field of natural language processing (NLP), which is a subfield of computer science (CS). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses machine learning (ML) and artificial intelligence (AI) techniques used in NLP, which makes cs.AI and cs.LG (Learning) likely sub-categories as well. The paper also touches on information retrieval (IR) and social influence (SI) in peer review, which makes cs.IR and cs.SI possible sub-categories.
